The following validation checks should be made every day for each property and for each metric

For incremental values:

select metric as metric_from_previous_day
from FactFacebookPageStats t
where dim_property_id = ID_of_property and date = CURDATE()-1
and time_stamp = (select MAX(time_stamp) 
          			from FactFacebookPageStats tt
          			 where tt.dim_property_id	= t.dim_property_id 
                     and tt.dim_date_id = t.dim_date_id); 

select incremental_metric
from ImportedFacebookPageStatistics
where property_id = ID_of_property and date = CURDATE();

select metric as metric_from_current_day
from FactFacebookPageStats
where dim_property_id = ID_of_property and date = CURDATE()
and time_stamp = (select MAX(time_stamp) 
          			from FactFacebookPageStats tt
          			 where tt.dim_property_id	= t.dim_property_id 
                     and tt.dim_date_id = t.dim_date_id); 

Validate that: metric_from_previous_day + incremental_metric = metric_from_current_day 

For total values:

select total_metric
from ImportedFacebookPageStatistics
where property_id = ID_of_property and date = CURDATE();

select metric
from FactFacebookPageStats t
where dim_property_id = ID_of_property and date = CURDATE()
and time_stamp = (select MAX(time_stamp) 
          			from FactFacebookPageStats tt
          			 where tt.dim_property_id	= t.dim_property_id 
                     and tt.dim_date_id = t.dim_date_id); 

Validate that: total_metric = metric

Note that currently only the "followers" metric lists total values. The rest of the values are incremental.